    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140340/extras/aaa8152ce27bd7dd82d921c0d1920664.poster.avif?t=1736510270\" width=616 height=437 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140340/extras/aaa8152ce27bd7dd82d921c0d1920664.webm?t=1736510270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“通过技术的进步，我们发现了一种新型生命体，即个人电脑集成怪物，简称 PiMon。我们尚未确定它们存在了多久，也不知道它们是如何产生的。它们似乎只是以数字蛋的形式出现在某一天的桌面屏幕上。显而易见的是，计算机技术的进步让它们终于向我们展示了自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-这就是你的作用所在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你已被选为 PiMon 管理员。与你自己的 PiMon 交朋友、照顾它、玩耍吧。我们一起揭开这些神秘生物的诸多秘密吧！”- Pikon 教授</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140340/extras/23558b83c26ddadf513dd3e357770425.poster.avif?t=1736510270\" width=616 height=437 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140340/extras/23558b83c26ddadf513dd3e357770425.webm?t=1736510270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>                                                                                                                                                        </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PiMon 只占用屏幕的一小部分。它们有自己的房间。您可以将这些房间移动到屏幕的顶部、底部或任何位置。您甚至可以放大或缩小屏幕！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                                        </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140340/extras/cb5cfd1cb9c23754776fc19a9922f8c6.poster.avif?t=1736510270\" width=616 height=437 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140340/extras/cb5cfd1cb9c23754776fc19a9922f8c6.webm?t=1736510270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想要更直接地与你的 PiMon 互动吗？与您的 PiMon 或宠物一起玩游戏，并使用 积极玩耍功能梳理它的皮毛！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                                        </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140340/extras/fa14d48831083cf8bc7449321e4b9fa7.poster.avif?t=1736510270\" width=800 height=567 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140340/extras/fa14d48831083cf8bc7449321e4b9fa7.webm?t=1736510270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您还可以通过 蒸汽的远程同乐功能或其他屏幕共享工具，在激动人心的 PvP 战斗中与好友一较高下，测试您的 派蒙实力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                                        </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140340/extras/44b90f16fe0d6d42d37907fb8cf05b1f.poster.avif?t=1736510270\" width=616 height=437 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140340/extras/44b90f16fe0d6d42d37907fb8cf05b1f.webm?t=1736510270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的 PiMon 可以更新并进化为新版本！目前，我们确信 PiMon 可以升级到 4.0 版。但有理由相信它们可以进一步更新！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所以，希望您能加入我们，发现有关 PiMon 的更多信息，管理员！</p>",
